<item>
            <title>[LU-4919] LFSCK first_failure_count is not correct</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4919</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running LFSCK and there are inodes/objects that cannot be fixed, the first_failure_count should not be zero. Yet, in the following output, we see that there are objects that can&apos;t be fixed, but the first_failure_position = 0&lt;/p&gt;

